Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how long are you going to sleep? School's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... There are other ways of waking me up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... I need you for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you should talk when you ask a favor of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the fuss? This is a very good thing for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the skeptical look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do so, first I want you to come to the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you have to bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... If I remember correctly, you're from the class next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, Sanae... I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Ahh! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Elen's friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fujieda. I'm Mio Fujieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know Sanae as well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.... I was in the same class as her the first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. By the way, is there something you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... well... actually, there's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to ask something about Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... what I'd like to ask is... about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you wouldn't want to go out with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's... you mean... Uhm... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother... what're you doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who you were talking to. Did you know Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for Mio. I've got a craving for Kanekoya's waffles,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wondered if she wanted to join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... have errands to do today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I interrupt something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, Fujiwara told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujieda, you mean. But hey, really? Mio said she likes you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... yeah... sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... she's got unusual tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what did you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came in before I said anything. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she wants to hear your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm the one who interrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no way you should leave things like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I went to all the trouble to arrange it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be such a bungler?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have done as we discussed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have just said "I like you. Be my boyfriend."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, get him to nod even if it means you have to choke him. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes 5 seconds. When confessing love, shock and awe is the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dragging your feet like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, come on! This is the last spring of your high school life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to ruin it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good timing! I was about to go look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good you found me, then. I wanna talk to Fujieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Good Sir, I'll just disappear as you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to your discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... What re you doing, Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujieda... uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the response to what you said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since it was out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I wanted to start as a friend for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a typical response. You have no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So have you made any plans with that friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to go into town tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a good job escorting Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my friend. If you do things to embarrass her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving you support, too. Mio is a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I realized that just from what little we talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... give me emergency allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already given you this month's allowance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a promise to go out on a date already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big achievement for a late bloomer like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you girls talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ms. Fujieda! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Fujieda, something major happened! It's big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, Mio is going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... it must be a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How did you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Now I'd give you 40%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a low score.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat what I taught you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not money that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a gigolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the lunch. It was very delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I would invite you to a restaurant or something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live alone with Elen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of my parents died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It happened when we were small... so I'm over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong. I live alone with my mother, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seeing her busy with work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,makes me wish... my father was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should support your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you need a guys help, I'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thanks!
