Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs34\bord0\fnAkbar\b0\c&H5B5339&\frz340.247\pos(429,689)}Movie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like Sanae's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\bord0\fnAkbar\b0\c&H5B5339&\frz348.698\pos(699,103)}Movie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\bord0\fnAkbar\b0\c&H5B5339&\frz345.391\pos(598,448)}Go to the kind of place\Nyou don't talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Go to the kind of place you don't talk about"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this "place you don't talk about"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb the stairs to adulthood and now you're Cinderella.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you clear all the schedules I created,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,today's date will be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn Sanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a woman, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that she's riding such a big motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always being poor, such an amazing bike is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of a 9mm Parabellum fired with a silencer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,awoke me... from a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We traveled from Mexico to Peru via land...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then to the Philippines via Palau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:10:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's been 6 months since we came to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to live on here... in this town, leaving our past behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we came to this country, you've... really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could see that your heart was rapidly opening up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that's how... a homeland is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pursuer has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But I received a silent warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The time we awake from this dream has come, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I wanted you to stay in the dream forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving the past behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:10:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... I'm not done with my penance yet, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your penance? Who are you repenting to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Directly to God... since I should be able to see him someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Inferno... has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to do this, but I'll take advantage of Mio's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio's parents got separated right after she was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father disappeared and is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio grew up being told that and still believes that lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father is a big shot who even appears in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiten Godo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:12:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The head of the Godo Family, a crime syndicate that covers a wide area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godo Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. "Fujieda" is her mother's maiden name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Godo Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even within the Godo Family, only a handful people have been told about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiten Godo wanted to protect his divorced wife and his daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the power struggle, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Mio is Daisuke Godo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, his half sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiten Godo absolutely never lets his daughter get dragged into violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet he can't openly protect her, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio is Kaiten's biggest weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come across such information?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe Master told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it was quite a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Master ran away from Inferno, he hid here in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you about it before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time, Master investigated the Godo Family thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he too intended to take advantage of their weakness when push came to shove.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakness? Don't tell me, Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to use Mio for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can be at least a trump card in an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The senior member who holds the real power in the Family now is Toru Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a member of Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the one who appeared in front of you was Inferno,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as we have Mio...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I should have told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known Mio would come to have feelings for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known our pursuers would come this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This life didn't last as long as I hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also have to get ready... to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you're right. We have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to cry at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back to being your old self now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of course that I should be prepared for little things like this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as we're being pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... You had forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was... happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During this 6 months, your smile... your face while you were sleeping at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you really looked happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to feel happy by just looking at you being happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one's birthplace can heal them this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought someday, I, too, would...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed about it by thinking that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you promised me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'll find a homeland for me someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the happiness you've felt up until now to be a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can return someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we leave, it's not like this country will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we can come back again will definitely come one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we can get a normal life back in a real sense will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that it's not that time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Reiji went home in the middle of your date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also he did say an urgent matter arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the young who celebrate the joys of youth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing more important than romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after I went to the trouble of coming up with a schedule for you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? "I guess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Speak of the devil... the very man who ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji, I had a good time yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take care of the urgent matter okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dodged my attack. You're quite good... But I'm better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to talk to Elen, so I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Where're you going, leaving your girlfriend here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... did that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's different somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems different... from usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... Why? Why is she in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... More importantly, is that really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or... should I say ex-Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
